Package: autoplotly
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Generation of Interactive Visualizations for
        Statistical Results
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: person("Yuan", "Tang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
        "terrytangyuan@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0001-5243-233X"))
Description: Functionalities to automatically generate interactive
        visualizations for statistical results supported by
        'ggfortify', such as time series, PCA, clustering and survival
        analysis, with 'plotly.js' <https://plotly.com/> and 'ggplot2'
        style. The generated visualizations can also be easily extended
        using 'ggplot2' and 'plotly' syntax while staying interactive.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/terrytangyuan/autoplotly
